  "body": "Project public URL https://hack.ethglobal.co/showcase/lodestar-light-client-recElTbWnTEw2ehQL\r\n\r\n- [x] 1. Light client server\r\n  - [x] a. Light Client Update creation https://github.com/ChainSafe/lodestar/pull/2494\r\n  - [x] b. Sync API - (depends on 1a) (Lion) https://github.com/ChainSafe/lodestar/pull/2494\r\n  - [x] c. Proof API - Request/response proofs API and proof serialization (Cayman, PR open that will unblock a light client) \r\n- [x] 2. Light client client (able to hit consumer endpoints, sync state machine)\r\n  - [x] a. Consume update and sync (Lion, simple/naive approach https://github.com/ChainSafe/lodestar/pull/2400) \"fast\" with mock backed https://github.com/ChainSafe/lodestar/pull/2494\r\n  - [x] b. Consume proofs and display partial data (Cayman) https://github.com/ChainSafe/lodestar/pull/2493\r\n  - [x] c. test sync and proof interaction https://github.com/ChainSafe/lodestar/pull/2494\r\n  - [x] d. Combine into a website (no style, eg https://yieldfarming.info/) https://github.com/ChainSafe/lodestar/pull/2494\r\n- [x] 3. Implement Altair fork on beacon node\r\n  - [x] a. State transition\r\n  - [x] b. State transition fast (optimize)(Cayman) https://github.com/ChainSafe/lodestar/pull/2508\r\n  - [x] c. Update validator flow (Tuyen, refresh of block + attestation creation)\r\n    - [x] 1. Beacon node server https://github.com/ChainSafe/lodestar/pull/2514 https://github.com/ChainSafe/lodestar/pull/2521 https://github.com/ChainSafe/lodestar/pull/2522\r\n    - [x] 2. Validator client (includes adding sync committee services and extra signatures) https://github.com/ChainSafe/lodestar/pull/2520\r\n  - [x] d. Networking\r\n    - [x] 1. Gossip https://github.com/ChainSafe/lodestar/pull/2479 https://github.com/ChainSafe/lodestar/pull/2519\r\n    - [x] 2. Request/response (Lion) https://github.com/ChainSafe/lodestar/pull/2444\r\n    - [x] 3. Discv5 https://github.com/ChainSafe/lodestar/pull/2484\r\n\r\n- [ ] 4. Bonus: Smuch it all together\r\n  - [x] Add sim tests for Altair with ALTAIR_FORK_EPOCH = 0\r\n  - [x] Add sim tests for Altair fork transition with ALTAIR_FORK_EPOCH = 2\r\n  - [x] Run a local devnet with Altair\r\n  - [x] Interop with Teku (already Altair capable)\r\n  - [x] Implement Lightclient producer code (https://github.com/ChainSafe/lodestar/pull/2494) in the real BeaconNode ",
